# GitHub Actions Workflows

This pack provides GitHub Actions CI/CD workflows for {{projectName}}.

## Workflows

- **CI** - Continuous Integration (lint, test, build)
- **CD** - Continuous Deployment
- **PR** - Pull Request checks
- **Release** - Release automation

## Usage

These workflows are automatically triggered on:
- Push to main branch
- Pull requests
- Release tags

## Configuration

Update workflow files in `.github/workflows/` to customize:
- Build steps
- Test commands
- Deployment targets
- Environment variables